      <remarks>
         <p>This EXPERIMENTAL and DRAFT file exteneds OSCAL to meet ATARC requirements.</p>
         <p>It provides the extensions, defined identifiers, and acceptable values in a machine-readable format necssary.</p>
         <p>They realize a mapping between OSCAL requirements for a FedRAMP SSP component and test criteria and testing tools part of the MITRE Security Automation Framework (SAF).</p>
      </remarks>
